hose that deal force damage.</p></tr></td><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Regeneration&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The wraith regains 5 hit points whenever it starts its turn and has at least 1 hit point. Whenever the wraith takes radiant damage, it loses this trait until the start of its next turn.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Regeneration</b> <b></b></p><p>The wraith regains 5 hit points whenever it starts its turn and has at least 1 hit point. Whenever the wraith takes radiant damage, it loses this trait until the start of its next turn.</p></tr></td><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Spawn Wraith&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;When the wraith kills a humanoid, that humanoid becomes a vortex wraith the start of this wraith’s next turn. The new wraith appears in the space where the humanoid died or in the nearest unoccupied square, and it rolls a new initiative check. The new wraith acts under the Dungeon Master’s control.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Spawn Wraith</b> <b></b></p><p>When the wraith kills a humanoid, that humanoid becomes a vortex wraith the start of this wraith’s next turn. The new wraith appears in the space where the humanoid died or in the nearest unoccupied square, and it rolls a new initiative check. The new wraith acts under the Dungeon Master’s control.</p></tr></td><tr><td><h4><b>Standard</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;(⚔) &lt;b&gt;Spiral Strike&lt;/b&gt; (force) ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Attack:&lt;/i&gt; Melee 1 (one creature); +12 vs. Fortitude&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hit:&lt;/i&gt; 2d8 + 6 force damage, and the target is slowed until the end of the wraith’s next turn.&lt;/p&gt;]] (⚔) <b>Spiral Strike</b> (force) ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p><i>Attack:</i> Melee 1 (one creature); [[/roll 1d20+12[ vs. Fortitude]#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;(⚔) &lt;b&gt;Spiral Strike&lt;/b&gt; (force) ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Attack:&lt;/i&gt; Melee 1 (one creature); &lt;u&gt;+12 vs. Fortitude&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;]]</p><p><i>Hit:</i> [[/roll 2d8 + 6#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;(⚔) &lt;b&gt;Spiral Strike&lt;/b&gt; (force) ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hit:&lt;/i&gt; 2d8 + 6 force damage, and the target is slowed until the end of the wraith’s next turn.&lt;/p&gt;]] <15>  force damage, and the target is slowed until the end of the wraith’s next turn.</p></tr></td><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\"&gt;⚔ &lt;b&gt;Spectral Helix&lt;/b&gt; (force) ✦ &lt;b&gt;Encounter&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Attack:&lt;/i&gt; Melee 2 (one creature); +12 vs. Reflex&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hit:&lt;/i&gt; 3d6 + 3 force damage, and the target takes ongoing 10 force damage and is immobilized (save ends both).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Miss:&lt;/i&gt; Half damage.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Effect:&lt;/i&gt; The vortex wraith can shift 1 square to a square adjacent to the target.&lt;/p&gt;]] ⚔ <b>Spectral Helix</b> (force) ✦ <b>Encounter</b></p><p><i>Attack:</i> Melee 2 (one creature); [[/roll 1d20+12[ vs. Reflex]#&lt;p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\"&gt;⚔ &lt;b&gt;Spectral Helix&lt;/b&gt; (force) ✦ &lt;b&gt;Encounter&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Attack:&lt;/i&gt; Melee 2 (one creature); &lt;u&gt;+12 vs. Reflex&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;]]</p><p><i>Hit:</i> [[/roll 3d6 + 3#&lt;p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\"&gt;⚔ &lt;b&gt;Spectral Helix&lt;/b&gt; (force) ✦ &lt;b&gt;Encounter&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hit:&lt;/i&gt; 3d6 + 3 force damage, and the target takes ongoing 10 force damage and is immobilized (save ends both).&lt;/p&gt;]] <13.5>  force damage, and the target takes ongoing 10 force damage and is immobilized (save ends both).</p><p><i>Miss:</i> Half damage.</p><p><i>Effect:</i> The vortex wraith can shift 1 square to a square adjacent to the target.</p></tr></td><tr><td><h4><b>Move</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Shadow Glide&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;Encounter&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Effect:&lt;/i&gt; The wraith shifts up to 6 squares.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Shadow Glide</b> ✦ <b>Encounter</b></p><p><i>Effect:</i> The wraith shifts up to 6 squares.</p></tr></td><tr><td><h4><b>Triggered</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\"&gt;ᗕ &lt;b&gt;Final Vortex&lt;/b&gt; (force, teleportation) ✦ &lt;b&gt;Encounter&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Trigger:&lt;/i&gt; The wraith drops to 0 hit points.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Attack (No Action):&lt;/i&gt; Close burst 5 (enemies in the burst); +12 vs. Reflex&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hit:&lt;/i&gt; 2d8 + 6 force damage, and the wraith teleports the target up to 5 squares and knocks it prone.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Miss:&lt;/i&gt; Half damage.&lt;/p&gt;]] ᗕ <b>Final Vortex</b> (force, teleportation) ✦ <b>Encounter</b></p><p><i>Trigger:</i> The wraith drops to 0 hit points.</p><p><i>Attack (No Action):</i> Close burst 5 (enemies in the burst); [[/roll 1d20+12[ vs. Reflex]#&lt;p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\"&gt;ᗕ &lt;b&gt;Final Vortex&lt;/b&gt; (force, teleportation) ✦ &lt;b&gt;Encounter&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Attack (No Action):&lt;/i&gt; Close burst 5 (enemies in the burst); &lt;u&gt;+12 vs. Reflex&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;]]</p><p><i>Hit:</i> [[/roll 2d8 + 6#&lt;p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\"&gt;ᗕ